parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as well as damage to property and other vehicles.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly accelerates without warning
often when the brake pedal is pressed or when the vehicle is in gear. The acceleration can be rapid and uncontrollable
leading to loss of control and accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Erratic acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities, as well as damage to property and other vehicles.
symptoms: often hesitating or surging forward without warning. The acceleration can be unpredictable and uncontrollable
leading to loss of control and accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: airbag failure to deploy in a crash
injuries sustained in a crash due to airbag failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag light being on can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in a crash.
Cracking of the dashboard can affect the operation of the airbag system and create a distraction while driving.
Sudden acceleration can lead to loss of control of the vehicle, resulting in accidents and injuries.

The cracking and melting of the dashboard can cause glare on the windshield, making it difficult to see while driving, and potentially leading to accidents. Additionally, the cracks may affect the deployment of airbags in the event of an accident.
symptoms: causing glare on the windshield; the cracks are spreading and getting worse over time; the dashboard is melting and becoming soft to the touch.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: even when the brake pedal is pressed; the vehicle jumps onto a curb or crashes into an object.
